          Professional Reliability
        </h4>
        <p>
          Punctual setup, backup equipment, and seamless execution ensure your
          event runs smoothly from start to finish.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-midnight-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-midnight-700">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neon-teal mb-3">
          Custom Curation
        </h4>
        <p>
          Every playlist is personally crafted based on your preferences, guest
          demographics, and event timeline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-midnight-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-midnight-700">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neon-teal mb-3">
